<p>[Page 24]</p>
<p>heavy rainstorm flooding trenches etc.</p>
<p>Sunday 19.5.18. Parcel from Florrie&nbsp; Sent Doff some Lace&nbsp; Wrote Doff.</p>
<p>Monday 20.5.18. Orders received &amp; Battn moved into Reserve in Ribemont area.</p>
<p>Tuesday 21.5.18&nbsp; Reconnoitred area- Battn working at night- saw Wisdom re left flank.</p>
<p>Wednesday 22.5.18. Visited by Yank General&nbsp; Battn. working at night</p>
<p>Thursday 23.5.18&nbsp; Battn working at night&nbsp; Hun Gas shelling- for two hours.</p>
<p>Friday 24.5.18. Order to relieve front on Sunday received.</p>
